query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(mc t) */ select min(chn.name) AS uncredited_voiced_character,
min(t.title)
from movie_companies AS mc
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2010
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND ci.note not like '%(voice)%' AND ci.note like '%(uncredited)%'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id;
